#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Smooth vectorfield]

Let $M$ be a #link("009D")[smooth manifold]. A _vectorfield_ is a #link("009G")[smooth map] $X: M -> T M $ into the #link("009P")[tangent bundle] such that for all points $x$ in $M$ $X(x) in T_(x) M $, or equivalently such that the _footpoint projection_ $p$ after $X$ is the identity.
